{"tid":620800,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣好怕死","createTime":"2018-04-07T18:43:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T20:51:19.000Z","uid":140754,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"64a6b605f9964a6bd91a7d16f70baeb19b0693f0","tid":620800,"uid":140754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T18:43:07.000Z","msg":"由細細個己經好怕死亡嘅感覺<br />\n好怕會死得好痛<br />\n好怕死後落十八層地獄受苦<br />\n好怕死後陰陽相隔會好孤獨<br />\n如今廿幾歲人都仲會驚<br />\n一諗起自己距離死亡又近一步個心就會好寒<br />\n可能一直以來身邊親人都係死於非命<br />\n一係癌症 一係撞車死<br />\n我覺得死亡係件好可怕好可怕嘅事<br />\n又冇可能逃避嘅事  人終須一死<br />\n有冇人明我講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61df920481da33f7caee43e0ae9b7216022d5699","tid":620800,"uid":11506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T18:44:07.000Z","msg":"好同意頭6句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae9bbb01a23c06c354694e6355951b38418dcb3b","tid":620800,"uid":6294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T18:46:26.000Z","msg":"好怕痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"409a251483fd47fc3615aff0a4abb0fd4da274fc","tid":620800,"uid":154661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T18:48:34.000Z","msg":"由八歲驚到依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a156299735c94861d416b849223be185d788166c","tid":620800,"uid":174074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T18:49:32.000Z","msg":"雖然好老土但人生在世<br />\n唯有係生前做多啲有意義而自己又鍾意做嘅野"},{"pid":"ce50201fdee0ee6adec4f877e8efbc000da2d4e4","tid":620800,"uid":140754,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T18:50:20.000Z","msg":"有時訓唔著就會亂諗<br />\n好容易就會諗到死<br />\n然後又驚一大餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7822e5b2f754edfb1dff9b27acdadcbdd763ae4b","tid":620800,"uid":181064,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T19:02:27.000Z","msg":"我唔驚死，因為我估同訓左覺差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我反而驚死之前嘅折磨，唔好燒死呀浸死呀...或者撞車斷左一半痛勁耐先死"},{"pid":"4f981a7963fa21c992ce4cf2ab0d0aa83b16a6df","tid":620800,"uid":58167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7822e5b2f754edfb1dff9b27acdadcbdd763ae4b","tid":620800,"uid":181064,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T19:02:27.000Z","msg":"我唔驚死，因為我估同訓左覺差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我反而驚死之前嘅折磨，唔好燒死呀浸死呀...或者撞車斷左一半痛勁耐先死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T19:11:38.000Z","msg":"Agger! 死前一定好痛苦"},{"pid":"e842d348bed5c8308af232fca19b428afbf4c82f","tid":620800,"uid":48358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T19:17:06.000Z","msg":"有錢就怕啫 <br />\n無錢驚乜撚"},{"pid":"79c320e80ef20acecf164bb8f47c391369a940c3","tid":620800,"uid":17232,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T19:19:25.000Z","msg":"樓主你只係驚緊死附帶嘅野，例如死後去邊，死嘅痛苦。<br />\n<br />\n其實有啲人單純咁驚死亡先係最恐怖"},{"pid":"a0e9748fd5ea9b04082d63e4aaf8600fcc4f2ee6","tid":620800,"uid":140754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e842d348bed5c8308af232fca19b428afbf4c82f","tid":620800,"uid":48358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T19:17:06.000Z","msg":"有錢就怕啫 <br />\n無錢驚乜撚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T19:19:38.000Z","msg":"有錢人死後就一定唔會落地獄架啦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"607f6468a91d7ae4eaebdd7abed7c5bb27df7052","tid":620800,"uid":140754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79c320e80ef20acecf164bb8f47c391369a940c3","tid":620800,"uid":17232,"like":2,"